---
@META
dir: skillsPraut/scripts
updated: 2026-04-15
files: 2 (extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs, install-skill.sh)
stack: Node.js ESM, Bash

@EXPORTS
extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs: CLI — regex-scans Phosphor regular style.css → phosphor-glyphs.json
install-skill.sh: CLI — symlinks skills/remotion → ~/.claude/skills/remotion

@VARS_CONSTANTS
styleCssPath: ../phosphor-icons/Fonts/regular/style.css (external sibling, NOT in working tree)
outPath: ../src/components/icons/phosphor-glyphs.json
GLYPH_REGEX: /\.ph\.ph-([a-z0-9-]+):before\s*\{\s*content:\s*"\\([0-9a-fA-F]+)";?\s*\}/g
SKILL_DIR: $HOME/.claude/skills/remotion
SCRIPT_DIR: <repo>/skillsPraut/skills/remotion

@FUNCTIONS
extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs() → void
  purpose: parse style.css → phosphor-glyphs.json (~1530 entries)
  side-effects: file (writes src/components/icons/phosphor-glyphs.json)
install-skill.sh() → void
  purpose: symlink skills/remotion to ~/.claude/skills/remotion
  side-effects: file (creates symlink)

@PROCESSES
glyph-extraction: read style.css → regex match `.ph-<name>:before { content: "\<hex>" }` → map name→unicode → write JSON
skill-install: detect symlink → skip if present | create symlink otherwise → available as /remotion skill

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: ../src/components/icons/ (write target)
external: node:fs, node:path, node:url (stdlib only), bash

@STANDARDS
- ESM script (.mjs) | exit 1 if no glyphs extracted
- Install script idempotent — safe re-run
- Symlink preferred over copy — auto-propagate updates
- Run: bun run extract-glyphs

@WARNINGS
- phosphor-icons/ sibling directory required by glyph script but NOT in working tree
  → must be cloned/downloaded separately for glyph refresh to succeed
- phosphor-glyphs.json committed; script is refresh-only
